# Card Vault — local-dev-only auto-open/auto-save.
#
# Set this to an absolute path on YOUR machine to have Card Vault load (and
# save back to) that Excel file automatically — no "Open Excel file..." click
# needed. Leave unset/blank to keep the normal manual open/add screen.
#
# This ONLY works with the local Vite dev server (`npm run dev`) or
# `vite preview` — Node can read your filesystem there. It has NO effect on
# the deployed Vercel site, which serves static files with no server process
# able to read a local path; that will always show the manual screen.
#
# Do NOT prefix this with VITE_ — that would bake the path into the client
# bundle. Copy this file to `.env.local` (already gitignored, never commit
# your real path) and fill in the value:
CARD_VAULT_PATH=
